notes.body: Hello,      Greetings from PharmEasy!     I understand your concern is regarding the order ID 656151038168170496-86180. I am sorry for the unpleasant experience that you had with this order. It was never our intention to upset you by any means.     I have highlighted the issue to the partner retailer team. We will respond with the update as soon as we receive any from them.  ​   I can see your order is in process, and the medicines are being arranged. The processing phase of your order has been delayed, as it is taking time to arrange the medicines from your order. Please accept my sincere apologies for the inconvenience caused to you     I noticed 2 quantities of the requested medicine, INDITEL AM 40MG STRIP OF 15 TABLETS are limited in stock. Our partner retailer is trying to arrange for the same from nearby retailers and from every possible source. We are unable to commit a timeframe by which it can be arranged.     However, you have an option to delete the unavailable medicine to avoid further delays in the delivery. Or you can wait till the medicines are arranged.     Please confirm if you wish to delete the said medicine. If the said medicine is deleted, there is a possibility that there might be some changes in the delivery charges and/or the promo code if applied.      I appreciate your patience in the meantime.     Regards,  Sandhya Nackwal

notes.body: Hello Ashish,     Greetings from PharmEasy!     With regards to promotional notifications, we always try to keep our customers updated on our offers. However, we apologize for the inconvenience caused due to our promotional messages.     Please be assured, I have forwarded your request to unsubscribe your number '9773944304' from getting the promotional notifications. It will take 3 working days to process it completely. You will only receive your order-related information. Also, if you have a dual sim phone, I would request you to help us with the second number as well, we will forward a request for the other number as well.      Further, if you wish to unsubscribe from getting the promotional notifications on your email id too, I request you to open your latest promotional email and hit unsubscribe at the bottom right-hand side corner to stop email promotions.     I certainly hope this helps, and I appreciate your understanding and patience in the meantime.     For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the Need Help section.     Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!     Regards,  Habiba
notes.body_html:
Hello Ashish,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

With regards to promotional notifications, we always try to keep our customers updated on our offers. However, we apologize for the inconvenience caused due to our promotional messages.

Please be assured, I have forwarded your request to unsubscribe your number '9773944304' from getting the promotional notifications. It will take 3 working days to process it completely. You will only receive your order-related information. Also, if you have a dual sim phone, I would request you to help us with the second number as well, we will forward a request for the other number as well. 

Further, if you wish to unsubscribe from getting the promotional notifications on your email id too, I request you to open your latest promotional email and hit unsubscribe at the bottom right-hand side corner to stop email promotions.

I certainly hope this helps, and I appreciate your understanding and patience in the meantime.

For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the Need Help section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!

Regards,
Habiba

notes.body: Hello Chandan Mishra,     Greetings from PharmEasy!      With referance to below mail.  ​For the Free Doctor Consultation offer after completing your order. We are happy to guide you on how to avail this benefit: Visit the “My Orders” section in your account. Locate the relevant order and click on the Free Doctor Consultation option. A coupen code will be displayed on the screen. Use Coupen code to proceed further and select your preferred doctor, along with the date and time for the consultation. Once you have selected the date and time, click on “Place Order”. Your consultation will then be scheduled without any payment.  Please note: This option will only be visible for orders where the Free Doctor Consultation offer was available at the time of placing the order.  For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.   Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!  Regards, Reshma Kokare PharmEasy

delivery status, not a generic apology.

Please treat this matter as urgent and resolve it *without any further
delay*.

Rishav
